1
00:00:55,130 --> 00:00:56,460
Was this the great cause

2
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:58,360
you faced back then?

3
00:00:58,700 --> 00:00:59,300
Mo'er,

4
00:01:00,130 --> 00:01:01,500
the most vicious poison in the world

5
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:03,300
is not arsenic or poisoned wine,

6
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,000
but trampling on human lives

7
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,200
in the name of immortality

8
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:08,000
and great causes.

9
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,000
Deputy Director Shen,

10
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:21,360
come with me to Ci'en Temple today.

11
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:29,800
Director,

12
00:01:36,259 --> 00:01:39,259
the smell of this water is not an ordinary ritual item.

13
00:01:39,660 --> 00:01:40,920
Deputy Director Shen,

14
00:01:41,030 --> 00:01:42,400
this is the Soul-Soothing Soup.

15
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,900
It can cleanse the dust in your heart.

16
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:45,229
During today's ritual,

17
00:01:45,460 --> 00:01:46,590
why not give it a try?

18
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:48,220
I have duties to attend to,

19
00:01:48,229 --> 00:01:49,830
so I need to stay awake and observe.

20
00:01:49,830 --> 00:01:51,229
I dare not be distracted.

21
00:01:58,060 --> 00:01:59,130
Over 300 people,

22
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:01,220
30% have already drunk it.

23
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:05,500
Her forehead is glowing.

24
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:17,900
Director,

25
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:19,760
I feel a bit stuffy.

26
00:02:20,260 --> 00:02:21,400
May I excuse myself for a moment?

27
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:21,930
Go ahead.

28
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:24,920
There is a quiet room in the back hall.

29
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:47,130
This is a restricted area.

30
00:02:47,130 --> 00:02:48,730
Trespassers will be killed.

31
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:53,060
I am the Deputy Director of the Imperial Astronomical Bureau,

32
00:02:53,060 --> 00:02:54,990
currently inspecting the temple.

33
00:02:57,060 --> 00:02:57,860
Stop.

34
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,600
Deputy Director Shen,

35
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:04,600
please follow me.

36
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,230
These are relics of eminent monks,

37
00:03:16,230 --> 00:03:18,360
the core for transferring soul power.

38
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,430
These medicinal materials

39
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:23,560
are identical to the ingredients of the Soul-Locking Pill in the Black Tower.

40
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,360
That's right.

41
00:03:24,460 --> 00:03:26,390
The holy water is brewed with this,

42
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:28,160
and a special primer is added.

43
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:32,200
The holy water contains hallucinogens and egg-like soul seeds.

44
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:34,030
Ci'en Temple is a soul power farm.

45
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:36,090
A soul power transmission pipeline.

46
00:03:37,100 --> 00:03:38,560
The ritual is about to end.

47
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,560
We should go back.

48
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,060
Deputy Director Shen,

49
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:42,400
what you saw today

50
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:43,600
is top secret.

51
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:46,160
I will keep my mouth shut.

52
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,130
Soul-Devouring Gu.

53
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,500
Its eggs are as small as dust

54
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:00,500
and dissolve in water.

55
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:01,830
It can control the mind.

56
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:07,690
It's Zhang Min.

57
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:17,360
I'm being watched.

58
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,360
Fixed step spacing.

59
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:34,330
Standard signs of a drug-controlled person.

60
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,500
Stop.
